\cvsection{SUMMARY}
8+ year in marketing and product, 5 with Amazon, specialized in product marketing, growth & demand generation, and product management.\\
\underline{Product Marketing}: positioning, core messaging, sales enablement, Go-to-market, thought leadership, advocacy, engagement, events, evangelism, perception.\\
\underline{Product Management}: end-to-end fundraising, pitch, team building, legal, and policy mediation, internal and external PR/AR, and launch.\\
\underline{Growth}: quantitative marketing investment, funnel optimization, SEM, outbound, re-targeting, P13N, attribution models, downstream and lifetime value, and analytics.\\


